[Njeri Wangari reviews](http://kenyanpoet.blogspot.com/2010/08/my-take-on-
ngugi-wa-thiongo.html) Ngugi Wa Thiongo's new autobiography: “Dreams in a Time
of War… let you get an understanding of Ngugi that you probably have never
before. We all to tend to think that Ngugi a radical who is too pragmatic
about use of his mothertongue only drawing his characters from his rural
setting…”

